    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Stop Dr. Corvid's Elemental Chaos</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dr. Corvid, a mad scientist with a penchant for chaos, has unleashed his latest experiment — the Virballs, virus-like creatures that manipulate elemental forces. Now, entire planets are overrun with these mischievous entities, spreading fire, wind, and electrical havoc across the galaxy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As ORB, an Object Removal Bot armed with rocket-powered claws, it’s up to you to track down these volatile creatures, harness their powers, and save the galaxy from Corvid’s creations before it’s too late.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Collect, Combine, and Conquer</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into this thrilling, action-packed platformer and stop the spread of Dr. Corvid’s chaos. Here’s what you’ll be doing in Virballs:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Capture and Combine</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab Virballs with ORB’s grappler claws and fuse their elemental properties — Earth, Water, Fire, Electricity, Air, and Slime — into unique hybrid weapons. Experiment with more than 40 different combinations to unlock powerful new ways to battle enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/a152d5527f011ac08b9c513ec8369605.poster.avif?t=1742309596\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/a152d5527f011ac08b9c513ec8369605.webm?t=1742309596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/a152d5527f011ac08b9c513ec8369605.mp4?t=1742309596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast-Paced Platformer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, and blast through levels packed with enemies, traps, and environmental puzzles. With ORB’s trusty blasters, thrusters, and claws, you’ll conquer every obstacle in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/55b30b03a0c9f67c294609508a4f547b.poster.avif?t=1742309596\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/55b30b03a0c9f67c294609508a4f547b.webm?t=1742309596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/55b30b03a0c9f67c294609508a4f547b.mp4?t=1742309596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Purge the Infested Worlds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six unique planets have been infested with Dr. Corvid’s Virballs. Each planet poses new threats and requires creative use of Virball powers to clear the infestation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/f733373c945fa8fe53bf752e9af93efa.avif?t=1742309596\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the Floobers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The adorable, peaceful Floobers are in danger - help the Floober King rescue his people and evacuate to their ship!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/c9e1713b2befe59c7ab5059ef77453c8.poster.avif?t=1742309596\" width=478 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/c9e1713b2befe59c7ab5059ef77453c8.webm?t=1742309596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343110/extras/c9e1713b2befe59c7ab5059ef77453c8.mp4?t=1742309596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Epic Boss Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge ultra-powerful Virball bosses to unlock new elemental Cores, expanding ORB’s arsenal and unlocking even more devastating weapon combinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Growing Galactic Adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your journey in Steam Early Access, with more planets and missions added over time. The full game, featuring all six planets, launches in early 2025!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
